      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. BABETTE (1) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 1.75 lengths (29.59) behind Consigliere at Sandown. Leading chance again. DR. FANATICAL (8) jumped quickly from box seven to score (28.57) two back then drew the same last time but settled off pace and could manage only a 7 length 3rd at Sandown (30.32). Will give a great sight again. FANTASTIC ZOHAN (2) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at Warragul over 460m behind Lindenow Buster (26.24) in a Grade 4/5. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. UNLEASH THE LION (5) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
